# Agentic dev-substrate — local dev tooling, NEVER committed (Gabriel decision
# 2026-05-21; supersedes D-13 inversion). Cross-conversation state persists on
# the local filesystem, not git — gitignoring .context/state/ does NOT break
# /mega --bootstrap (state files live locally on Gabriel's dev machine). The
# only loss is fresh-clone-on-a-new-machine carrying no state, which is
# acceptable: the agentic substrate is dev-machine-bound tooling; the product
# ships via git. NOTE: docs/ is intentionally NOT listed here — pending Gabriel
# classification (dev-process docs vs product docs); see .context/state/WORRIES.md.
